"Before Copiloto Médico, Familjeläkarna teams were dealing with documentation backlogs caused by long dictations and manual transcription. This added stress and limited how many patients they could see each day."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"By introducing an AI clinical assistant, notes are generated during the visit, in a structured format and ready to review, instead of being pushed to the end of the day."}]]}]]}]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"border-t border-slate-100 bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-14 md:px-6 lg:px-0","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-2","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-4 text-sm text-slate-700","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-[20px] font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-[22px]","children":"Real‑time notes for the whole care team"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Copiloto Médico was deployed across different roles: physicians, nurses and mental health professionals. During each visit, the tool listens and proposes a structured clinical note draft that the professional only needs to review and complete."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"This way, attention stays on the conversation with the patient while documentation is prepared in the background."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-4 text-sm text-slate-700","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-[20px] font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-[22px]","children":"Time saved and more visits per day"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"mt-2 space-y-2 text-xs text-slate-700","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":["Around ",["$","span",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-slate-900","children":"5 minutes less"}]," of documentation per consultation."]}],["$","li",null,{"children":["Roughly ",["$","span",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-slate-900","children":"1 additional free hour"}]," per clinician each day."]}],["$","li",null,{"children":["Capacity t